## Next Step: Phase 2 вЂ” Backend API Structure

Once you approve this schema I will design:
- **Node.js/Express** route + controller architecture
- Auth middleware (JWT + refresh tokens + role guards)
- Financial engine service (double-entry writer, split calculator)
- AI service wrappers (OpenAI diet, MediaPipe form correction)
- Payment gateway adapter layer (Fawry, Instapay, Paymob, Vodafone Cash)
